body_html: @PINTO0309 sorry,I seem to have found the reason. At present, there are few OPS officially supported by tflite, so many complex models can not run on tflite. At present, only the mobilenet model has been successfully converted. Inception V3, ssd-mobilenet and other models can not be successfully converted by toco, because the op used in the model does not support it. I use the ssd-mobilenet model.What do you mean?
